data.description: 3 car garage! Don't miss this move-in ready captivating home in the highly sought-after Bridges. This 3BR/3BA+Den/Office, split plan backs to common space. 1bd has an ensuite. Open kitchen equipped w/ SS &  appliances and lrg pantry. The dining area is adjacent to the kitchen and perfect for hosting gatherings. The primary bedroom is spacious with large walk-in closet & an en suite bathroom with a lrg soaking tub. Step outside through multi slidert to a welcoming yard w/ no neighbors behind - just views!
